headlines.title: WCWS Game 3: Texas wins national championship, defeating Texas Tech, 10-4, powered by Mia Scott's grand slam
headlines.description: Mia Scott's fourth-inning grand slam was the decisive blow in leading the Longhorns to a women's softball national championship.

headlines.title: WCWS Game 3: Texas Tech vs. Texas softball live updates, highlights from the Women's College World Series
headlines.description: The Texas Tech Red Raiders tied up the series with a 4-3 victory over the Texas Longhorns on Thursday night. Who will win it all?

headlines.title: Aaron Rodgers signing is ‘worst-case scenario’ for Steelers: Ryan Clark
headlines.description: Ryan Clark thinks that the Steelers are making a mistake in signing Rodgers, saying that fans should look it as a "worst case scenario."

headlines.title: Diddy's ex-girlfriend 'Jane' testifies about pressure to participate in 'hotel nights'
headlines.description: "Jane" testified about her "love contract" with Sean "Diddy" Combs and feeling pressure to continue with the sexual encounters.

headlines.title: Deportees are being held in a converted shipping container in Djibouti, ICE says
headlines.description: Deported migrants have been stuck at a military base in Djibouti for over two weeks — and ICE officers are also there, guarding them 24 hours a day.

headlines.title: Buildup to a Meltdown: How the Trump-Musk Alliance Collapsed
headlines.description: President Trump’s decision to pull a close associate of Elon Musk’s out of the running to lead NASA helped doom an extraordinary partnership.

headlines.title: Supreme Court allows DOGE team to access Social Security systems
headlines.description: The Supreme Court has handed the Trump administration two victories in cases involving the Department of Government Efficiency, including giving it access to Social Security systems containing personal data on millions of Americans.

headlines.title: Resident Evil 9 officially unveiled, coming February
headlines.description: Capcom has lifted the lid on Resident Evil 9, the next entry in its long-standing horror series.

headlines.title: Sean 'Diddy' Combs trial day 22 recap: Witness says Combs participated in 'hotel nights' as recently as August 2024
headlines.description: Testifying through tears, the woman, using the pseudonym "Jane," told jurors Combs provided her drugs and forced her to participate in "freak-offs" or "hotel nights."

headlines.title: Kilmar Abrego Garcia is back in the U.S. to face criminal charges : NPR
headlines.description: Abrego Garcia faces criminal charges for allegedly transporting migrants without legal status around the country, according to a Justice Department indictment.
